3>Let's Talk About the Internet</h3></div></a><a href="https://thewalrus.ca/podcasts/#water" target="_self" id="hmenu_list_item_uni_36" class="hmenu_list_item hmenu_item_8 " style="color:#CCC; font-size:20px"><div class="hmenu_list_content"><h3>What About Water</h3></div></a><a href="https://thewalrus.ca/podcasts/#bandwidth" target="_self" id="hmenu_list_item_uni_35" class="hmenu_list_item hmenu_item_9 " style="color:#CCC; font-size:20px"><div class="hmenu_list_content"><h3>Bandwidth</h3></div></a><a href="https://thewalrus.ca/podcasts/#edgeofenergy" target="_self" id="hmenu_list_item_uni_34" class="hmenu_list_item hmenu_item_10 " style="color:#CCC; font-size:20px"><div class="hmenu_list_content"><h3>The Edge of Energy</h3></div></a><a href="https://thewalrus.ca/podcasts/#water" target="_self" id="hmenu_list_item_uni_37" class="hmenu_list_item hmenu_item_11 " style="color:#CCC; font-size:20px"><div class="hmenu_list_content"><h3>Courage Inc.</h3></div></a> </div> <div class="hmenu_col_devider"></div> </div> <!-- END: COL --><!-- BEGIN: COL --> <div class="hmenu_col_5 hmenu_custom_5 " data-type="list" data-id="4"> <div class="hmenu_inner_col hmenu_col_load"> <h2 class="hmenu_mega_bottom_border">The Walrus Lab</h2><a href="https://thewalrus.ca/partnerships/amazon-first-novel-award/" target="_self" id="hmenu_list_item_uni_43" class="hmenu_list_item hmenu_item_0 " style="color:#CCC; font-size:20px"><div class="hmenu_list_content"><h3>Amazon Canada First Novel Award</h3></div></a><a href="https://thewalrus.ca/the-walrus-lab/#whatwedo" target="_self" id="hmenu_list_item_uni_14" class="hmenu_list_item hmenu_item_1 " style="color:#CCC; font-size:20px"><div class="hmenu_list_content"><h3>What We Do</h3></div></a><a href="https://thewalrus.ca/the-walrus-lab/#ourservices" target="_self" id="hmenu_list_item_uni_15" class="hmenu_list_item hmenu_item_2 " style="color:#CCC; font-size:20px"><div class="hmenu_list_content"><h3>Our Services</h3></div></a><a href="https://thewalrus.ca/the-walrus-lab/#ourprojects" target="_self" id="hmenu_list_item_uni_16" class="hmenu_list_item hmenu_item_3 " style="color:#CCC; font-size:20px"><div class="hmenu_list_content"><h3>Our Projects</h3></div></a><a href="https://thewalrus.ca/newsletters" target="_self" id="hmenu_list_item_uni_17" class="hmenu_list_item hmenu_item_4 " style="color:#CCC; font-size:20px"><div class="hmenu_list_content"><h3>The Insider Newsletter</h3></div></a><a href="#" target="_self" id="hmenu_list_item_uni_39" class="hmenu_list_item hmenu_item_5 " style="color:#CCC; font-size:20px"><div class="hmenu_list_content"><h3></h3></div></a><a href="https://store.walrusmagazine.com/" target="_self" id="hmenu_list_item_uni_40" class="hmenu_list_item hmenu_item_6 icon_hero_default_thin_e611" style="color:#CCC; font-size:20px"><div class="hmenu_list_content"><h3>SHOP THE WALRUS</h3><span><img class="lazy" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201%201'%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-src="https://walrus-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/img/shop.gif"></span></div></a> </div> <div class="hmenu_col_devider"></div> </div> <!-- END: COL --> </div> </div> <!-- END: MEGA --> </li><li class=""><a href="https://thewalrus.ca/donate/" target="_self" title="" ><div class="hmenu_no_sub hmenu_wrap icon_hero_default_solid_e631 hmenu_nav_uni_61"><span>Donate</span></div></a><div class="hmenu_item_devider"></div></li><li class=""><a href="https://thewalrus.ca/subscribe/" target="_self" title="" ><div class="hmenu_no_sub hmenu_wrap icon_hero_default_solid_e61e hmenu_nav_uni_62"><span>Subscribe</span></div></a><div class="hmenu_item_devider"></div></li><li class="hmenu_mega_li hmenu_remove_mega_mobile hmenu_remove_mega "><a title=""><div class="hmenu_wrap icon_hero_default_thin_e645 hmenu_nav_uni_13 hmenu_mega_menu icon_hero_default_thin_e600"><span></span></div></a><div class="hmenu_item_devider"></div> <!-- BEGIN: MEGA --> <div class="hmenu_submenu hmenu_mega_sub hmenu_drop_devider" > <!-- 