<img class="lazy" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20150%20150'%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-src="https://walrus-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/img/jessica-johnson-new-headshot-bw.png" alt="Jessica Johnson" width="150px" align="left" style="padding-right:10px;">
<div>
Sincerely,<br />Jessica Johnson<br />Editor-in-Chief
