vg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201%201'%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-src="https://thewalrus.ca/wp-content/plugins/trust-indicators-master/includes/Trust-Logo-Stacked.svg" style="display:block;"> <div class="trust-indicators-title-wrap"></div></a></div><p>The Trust Project is a collaboration among news organizations around the world. Its goal is to create strategies that fulfill journalisms basic pledge: to serve society with a truthful, intelligent and comprehensive account of ideas and events.</p><a href="http://thetrustproject.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Learn more.</a></div><!-- /Widget Shortcode --><strong>Behind The Story</strong><!-- Widget Shortcode --><div id="trust_indicators_article-3" class="widget trust_indicators_article widget-shortcode area-arbitrary "><h2 class="widgettitle">Behind The Story</h2><p><strong>Type</strong>: Analysis</p><p>Analysis: Based on factual reporting, although it incorporates the expertise of the author/producer and may offer interpretations and conclusions.</p>
