<p><img class="wp-image-102038 alignleft lazy" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20197%2034'%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-src="https://walrus-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/img/TusksConvo-logo.png" alt="Walrus logo with tusks and Canada's Conversation" width="197" height="34" /><div class="su-spacer" style="height:2px"></div></p>
<p style="color:#fff; line-height: 1.3rem;">The Walrus is located within the bounds of Treaty 13 signed with the Mississaugas of the Credit. This land is also the traditional territory of the Anishnabeg, the Haudenosaunee, and the Wendat peoples.<br /> Read more on our <a href="https://thewalrus.ca/about/" style="text-decoration: underline">About Us page</a>.</p>
